---
---
<section id="portfolio" class="bg-[oklch(97%_0.004_250)] px-6 py-20 md:px-12 md:py-[120px]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1240px]">
    <div class="mb-14 max-w-[620px]" data-aos="fade-up">
      <span class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-primary">Trabalhos recentes</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3.5 font-display text-[28px] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)] md:text-[38px]">Projetos que resolveram um problema de verdade.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-[1.3fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div class="hover-lift-card flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[18px] border border-[oklch(90%_0.006_250)] bg-white shadow-[0_20px_40px_-24px_oklch(20%_0.02_250_/_0.15)] transition-all md:row-span-2" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="flex h-[220px] items-center justify-center bg-[repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,oklch(94%_0.02_258),oklch(94%_0.02_258)_10px,oklch(91%_0.025_258)_10px,oklch(91%_0.025_258)_20px)]">
          <span class="rounded-md border border-[oklch(88%_0.02_258)] bg-white px-3 py-1.5 font-mono text-xs text-[oklch(45%_0.05_258)]">print do projeto aqui</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-7 pb-8">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-primary">Landing page</span>
          <h3 class="my-2 font-display text-xl font-bold text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)]">Cliente exemplo — clínica odontológica</h3>
          <p class="m-0 text-[14.5px] leading-[1.55] text-[oklch(42%_0.012_250)]">Site institucional zerado, sem presença no Google. Nova landing page trouxe agendamentos direto pelo WhatsApp e primeira página no Google em 3 meses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hover-lift-card overflow-hidden rounded-[18px] border border-[oklch(90%_0.006_250)] bg-white shadow-[0_20px_40px_-24px_oklch(20%_0.02_250_/_0.15)] transition-all" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="80">
        <div class="flex h-[140px] items-center justify-center bg-[repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,oklch(94%_0.02_258),oklch(94%_0.02_258)_10px,oklch(91%_0.025_258)_10px,oklch(91%_0.025_258)_20px)]">
          <span class="rounded-md border border-[oklch(88%_0.02_258)] bg-white px-2.5 py-[5px] font-mono text-[11px] text-[oklch(45%_0.05_258)]">print aqui</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 pb-[26px]">
          <span class="text-[11.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-primary">Sistema sob medida</span>
          <h3 class="my-[7px] font-display text-[17px] font-bold text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)]">Cliente exemplo — distribuidora</h3>
          <p class="m-0 text-[13.5px] leading-[1.5] text-[oklch(42%_0.012_250)]">Controle de pedidos que era feito em planilha virou sistema próprio, cortando horas de retrabalho por semana.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hover-lift-card overflow-hidden rounded-[18px] border border-[oklch(90%_0.006_250)] bg-white shadow-[0_20px_40px_-24px_oklch(20%_0.02_250_/_0.15)] transition-all" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="160">
        <div class="flex h-[140px] items-center justify-center bg-[repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,oklch(94%_0.02_258),oklch(94%_0.02_258)_10px,oklch(91%_0.025_258)_10px,oklch(91%_0.025_258)_20px)]">
          <span class="rounded-md border border-[oklch(88%_0.02_258)] bg-white px-2.5 py-[5px] font-mono text-[11px] text-[oklch(45%_0.05_258)]">print aqui</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 pb-[26px]">
          <span class="text-[11.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.05em] text-primary">Landing page</span>
          <h3 class="my-[7px] font-display text-[17px] font-bold text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)]">Cliente exemplo — estúdio de arquitetura</h3>
          <p class="m-0 text-[13.5px] leading-[1.5] text-[oklch(42%_0.012_250)]">Portfólio online substituindo o Instagram como única vitrine, com formulário de contato direto.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
